Committee: Business and Labor
1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to claims against the state; to appropriate
2 funds for the payment of certain claims; to provide for payment of
3 the claims; to authorize agencies to write off certain claims as
4 prescribed; and to declare an emergency.
5 Be it enacted by the people of the State of Nebraska,
